And when catching and re-throwing in `CheckHealth`:

```cpp
// In CheckHealth()
try {
    RecreateRenderer();
} catch (const std::runtime_error& e) {
    std::string newErrorMsg = "Renderer recreation failed after health check: " + std::string(e.what());
